name: 9 Seconds of Waves #15
description:
Exploration of color and movement, using 16mm film.
-
Around 5 second (125f) of found footage archive printed to black and white film stock (Orwo PF2) and then printed using flat print technique to another b&w and color print stock (Kodak 3383). It's a copy of a copy, generation not traced.
-
15 of 19 in the series
